# {{PRODUCT_NAME}}

Product slug: `{{PRODUCT_SLUG}}`

## Quick start

```bash
# Environment
ruby -v   # Ruby 3+
node -v   # if backend/web stacks need Node

# Health of delivery wiring
ruby scripts/doctor.rb

# Validate idea/task/issue front matter
ruby scripts/validate_workflow.rb

# Run delivery checks for a task (after creating tasks/<name>.md)
ruby scripts/deliver.rb <task-name>
```

## Agent commands

See `COMMANDS.md`. Examples:

```text
想法 my-first-idea
产品 my-first-task
架构 my-first-task
后端 my-first-task
前端 my-first-task
测试 my-first-task
交付 my-first-task
```

